---
import { ArrowRight } from "lucide-react";
---

<section class="pt-32">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-2 md:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div
            class="grid overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-primary/30 md:grid-cols-2 bg-accent shadow-2xl"
        >
            <div class="my-auto px-6 py-10 sm:px-10 sm:py-12 lg:p-16">
                <div class="w-full md:max-w-md">
                    <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold lg:text-3xl">
                        Listo para llevar tu proyecto al siguiente nivel?
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-6 text-lg">
                        En
                        <span class="font-semibold text-primary">
                            Devs hub&ZeroWidthSpace;
                        </span>, ofrecemos soluciones personalizadas para
                        potenciar tu empresa o emprendimiento. Desde desarrollo
                        web y móvil hasta marketing digital, nuestro equipo de
                        expertos está listo para ayudarte a alcanzar tus
                        objetivos.
                    </p>
                    <button
                        data-slot="button"
                        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-all disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&_svg]:pointer-events-none [&_svg:not([class*='size-'])]:size-4 shrink-0 [&_svg]:shrink-0 outline-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow-xs hover:bg-primary/90 h-9 px-4 py-2 has-[>svg]:px-3 w-full md:w-fit"
                    >
                        <ArrowRight className="mr-2 size-5" />

                        Comienza tu asesoría gratuita
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div
                class="grid grid-cols-3 border-t border-primary/30 md:border-t-0 md:border-l"
            >
                <div
                    class="-mb-px flex items-center justify-center border-r border-b border-primary/30 p-5 nth-[3n]:border-r-0 sm:p-6"
                >
                    <img
                        src="/images/placeholder.svg"
                        alt="Logo 1"
                        class="size-12 object-cover object-center sm:size-16 lg:size-24"
                    />
                </div>
                <div
                    class="-mb-px flex items-center justify-center border-r border-b border-primary/30 p-5 nth-[3n]:border-r-0 sm:p-6"
                >
                    <img
                        src="/images/placeholder.svg"
                        alt="Logo 2"
                        class="size-12 object-cover object-center sm:size-16 lg:size-24"
                    />
                </div>
                <div
                    class="-mb-px flex items-center justify-center border-r border-b border-primary/30 p-5 nth-[3n]:border-r-0 sm:p-6"
                >
                    <img
                        src="/images/placeholder.svg"
                        alt="Logo 3"
                        class="size-12 object-cover object-center sm:size-16 lg:size-24"
                    />
                </div>
                <div
                    class="-mb-px flex items-center justify-center border-r border-b border-primary/30 p-5 nth-[3n]:border-r-0 sm:p-6"
                >
                    <img
                        src="/images/placeholder.svg"
                        alt="Logo 4"
                        class="size-12 object-cover object-center sm:size-16 lg:size-24"
                    />
                </div>
                <div
